data.description:
Check out this adorable 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home in the heart of Beverly Hills. Everything has been well maintained and kept up! Roof is 2011. New garage door 2019.
Located near shopping, restaurants, grocery stores and doctors! You have everything you may need within minutes of pulling out of the driveway.
